content.detailedDescription: Me and my family were driving from the cove palisades to madras oregon when i noticed a bright spot in the sky through my sunroof. we pulled over as soon as we could. i thought the object was a visible planet or star during the day at first or maybe a very small forming cloud. we know it was high in the sky because we drove about 15 miles and it was still in the same location and we could see it bright though a few cloud patches. it stayed in the same spot for about an hour everybody in my car was making sure to keep an eye on it, when we pulled in line to get coffee the object split into two. it seemed to all happen slowly. the object that separated from the original eventually turned into a pen shape and had two spots behind it. after the separation, 1 object came from an unknown area and flew around the 2 objects at high speed and made quick pinpoint turns and then disappeared. i watched as the pen shaped object left in another direction and the original object into another direction. i watched them as they slowly disappeared out of my vision because they became to small to see. if i was holding a bb at arms length that is how small it was at the beginning. they were not landing just moving into another region of airspace. i was a little scared after watching all of this and have been trying to come up with a reasonable explanation, but we can't and i am hoping somebody else had seen the same as we did in that area or anywhere else. the three pictures are what we saw at first.
content.summary: Looked like a star in the daytime then about an hour later it split into two. the one that split turned into a pen shape and they both started moving. a third one started to fly around the 2 that separated. definetely at high altitude.

content.summary: They appeared to change shape.  there was a big one, then little baby ones around the big one.

content.detailedDescription:
at about 10:00am i was in our backyard with my wife and my 21 year-old daughter. we live about four miles south of hill air force base.  hill conducts training fly-overs all the time, so seeing aircraft is commonplace. on this particular day an f-16 flew over drawing my attention.  thinking that i might see another, i looked to the north and up and spied a bright silvery object high in the air. it was moving very lazily from north to south and appeared to be bobbing about like a balloon. my daughter also saw it.

from time to time mylar balloons come untied and float away, so i thought what i was seeing was a balloon because object looked round and metallic because it glittered in the sky like silver mylar balloon.

as i watched the object, to my amazement, it suddenly stopped dead, moved a bit further to the south and then did a very tight and quick 180-degree turn and shot off in a direct line to the north, vanishing in under three seconds. i could not tell if it was going up, but it appeared to be, also.

for the record, i was raised in western washington in the middle of seattle boeing field, seatac international airport, mcchord afb, renton boeing field, paine field where the 747s are built and at least four regional airports. simply put, i have seen aircraft of all types. i even saw an sr-71 and a b-2 bomber in flight when they were not supposed to exist. thus, i think i have a pretty good understanding of how various types of aircraft look on the ground and in the air. i even worked at boeing field in seattle for three years.

what i saw was not an airplane by our standards. no aircraft that i have ever seen stops in midair and then pulls a turn that, to me, appeared to have a radius of the same length as the object was wide. an airplane would literally have to turn on a wingtip to make such a turn. 

my wife thought it might have been a helicopter. that is a possibility. helicopters can stop in midair and turn on their own axis, but the object seemed too high for any helicopter i have been around and definitely moved too fast of one when it disappeared.

i wish that i could have taken photos or a video, but the event happened too quickly.
content.summary: Ufo sighting over hill air force base in utah may 26, 2016

content.detailedDescription:
My boyfriend and i were heading south on highway 31 (aka nashville hwy) in columbia tn on friday may, 27, 2016 around 8:45 pm cdt. there was mid-level cloud cover. about 3 miles away, we saw a pinpoint of blue light and thought it was only an airplane/helicopter, but as we got closer, we noticed the object did not appear to move or change direction. we were even as close to driving under this point of light for around a minute or two. we pulled off to the shoulder of the road in front of spring hill high school. i managed to grab my phone, snap a photo and take some video of the object, but the video is only for a few seconds.

the brightest area was a bluish in color. there were tiny red lights blinking on each side.

i felt somewhat nervous. due to some heavy traffic on the highway, we had to keep moving. we lost sight of the object as we were driving away.

please note, photos sent are rather fuzzy due to glare. video is a bit short.
content.summary: Blue light w/red and white light that hovered over the road. did not move at all.

content.detailedDescription:
On the morning of march 7, 2016, a big thunderstorm with a lot of clouds and rain moved over west la at about 6:00am pst.  we were gathered in the parking lot at cheviot hills recreation park off of motor ave, to film a shot of a bus for a commercial we were shooting.  when the storm was near enough, and the lightning began, the crew retreated to our vehicles.  i was in the empty end of the lot and away from crew and the set (approx. 34.047831, -118.409431) and i wanted to catch some lightning on video.  

i didn't get any lightning but i did get this... is it a type of ball or globe lightning??  is that even a thing?  anyway it's all toward the top above the park field lights and the iphone camera is looking west. a triangle of lights and satellite lights circling the lower left light.
let me know what you thinké
content.summary: Light spheres in clouds during rain storm

content.detailedDescription:
there were two of us outside in our garden area between 8 to 9 pm. we were talking about the planet mars and on the local 6 pm news they mentioned that you could really see the planet very well tonight. i had walked outside of the garden area to the other side of our house to place some garbage in the can. i saw how much better you could see mars because there were no lights on in the other area of our house.
 we were looking all around us 360 degrees and focused on venus more in southwest sky, then at mars which was about 60 degrees in the sky from the southwest in alignment from venus.
 we were talking about how some stars seem to appear to have another one just behind them and that it was making them look bigger and brighter and then we talked about the app you could get on your phone to map the stars.
in an area that was about 30 degrees and more north from where mars was there were maybe 3 to 4 stars that were in that area and they were about the same in size, except for one that was a little brighter than the rest.
 all of a sudden within this little area there was a whole group of star like objects maybe 10 to 15 of them and they were all twinkling at different intervals!!! but then about four of them started making these little random jumps in the sky as they were moving to the southwest. then two of them made larger jumps in the sky and the others disappeared. the two remaining lights then disappeared and reappeared about 30 degrees from where we last saw them with the group. 
 we were absolutely amazed as we have never seen anything like this in the skies before. of the two of us, i'd taken astronomy classes and the other is retired from the major aerospace company in tucson. so, we have been privy to different types of launches that have occurred in our tucson skies. 
the two objects that were left continued on the southwestern path and they had pulsating lights on them, also there was no sound coming from these objects, they disappeared into the dark of the sky.
 we talked about what we'd just seen and the other person said that they thought at first that she was seeing lightning when the group first appeared. i was comparing the random twinkling to a certain type of firework that goes up into the air then explodes into a random white twinkling as it goes downward. these objects were in no way fireworks,they were traveling in a southwestern path. when the few of them did the sky jumping, light skipping if you will, i could see a light trail that was from the arch of the jump. we both felt light hearted because it seemed that the lights were kind of playing around. 
 as a point of reference, we came out after about an hour later and we saw two planes, they were much closer and traveling in different directions and we could both hear the sound that came from the motors. one was a small airplane and the other was a jet plane that was coming in to the tucson int'l airport.
content.summary: Saw several twinkling objects , then some made little forward dashses, then some completey jumped from one point to another, then tere were only two visible after they reappeared 30 degrees futher  from they we originally.

content.detailedDescription: On may 27,2016 at 0025hrs: i was in my bed watching tv when i heard my dog starting to start growling. as i got up to look out my window i saw green lights in the sky traveling towards me. its speed was approximately 60 mph. it appeared to be approximately 1000 ft high. as it got closer i could see the objects shape was cylindrical. there were numerous green lights around the perimeter of the front of the craft that were pulsating like a movie marquee. also the front of the craft was inverted with visible ribbed supports. the rear had red lights. it traveled from west to east.
A strange flighht object seen. took a spontaneuis photo.
content.summary: Large mother ship

content.detailedDescription: It was around 2 am when i felt that someone is calling me in kitchen. i entered in kitchen and found two humanoid entities at least 6 to 5 feat tall waiting for me. first i startled then a slowly i started feel calm as i know them and felt as if they are my parents. the lady humanoid was calm where as male was little tensed. the lady took a  double disc shaped with two antennas machine from no where and placed in utensil and rotated the disc and rotated the antenna. slowly it started to elevate and rotate. the most fascinating thing was it made the things made up of metals to elevate in air. she said that by placing this device in a utensil made up of particular can make the other things made up of similar things to elevate. then we three sat on floor for few seconds and i felt relaxed and calmed. then the lady entity and i went to drawing room and she saw into my eyes i don't know for how long then the male entity came and said that they have to leave. when the lady entity i sensed telepathically that she don't want me to leave here alone but was forced to do so. after that i found myself awake seated on my bed and the sun was rising.

content.detailedDescription: From my yard in southwest las vegas i looked up and thought jupiter looked considerably brighter and larger than usual.  noticed the object was moving.  this was nothing but a solid white light travelling slightly slower than the speed of a normal plane that you'd see at 30,000 feet (though much lower - estimate 5-10,000, possibly lower).  waited for blinking to see if it was an airplane but it wasn't.  i went in the house and grabbed my binoculars and watched for four or five minutes (almost directly overhead when first watched through binoculars).  this was a perfectly round bright, white light only, with no other lights and no discernible body.  as it passed over the city toward the northeast it looked a little more orange and as it got smaller i saw squiggling (like a kid playing with a flashlight).  i suppose this could have been "binocular error" although i peripherally had a star in the same field of vision and it wasn't squiggling. i felt amazed and curious and came right in to report this.  a lot of people had to see this (unless they were all texting).  the object disappeared from view eventually, not sure if this was literally or it became too small to see.
content.summary: Bright solid white light passed slowly overhead.

content.detailedDescription: My fiance booked a trip for us to go to lazy lane cabins and the first night we were there, we went outside to the front porch to sit down and talk. a few minutes went by and we heard a strange noise coming from the tree line. i looked up and didn't see any airplanes or anything that could be making the noise. the tree line was shaking like there was wind blowing even though there wasn't wind blowing. we heard the noise for about 15 seconds and then the noise vanished. i have never in my entire life heard a noise like this before. it was not an airplane, helicopter or any known aircraft that i have ever personally heard.
content.summary: My fiance and i were sitting on the front porch and heard a strange noise

content.detailedDescription: While driving my car around 3 a.M. to get my baby asleep, i noticed the three orbs in the sky. i disregarded them and kept driving. when making my second round through the same area, i noticed the three orbs where in the same spot. i thought that i may have been too sleepy to really know, so i stopped in the road and starred for approximately 2-3 minutes and realized they weren't moving. i was on the phone with a friend and the call kept dropping but i was detailing to him what i was seeing. i decided to go another round and saw that the orbs were still in the same spot. i pulled over again and noticed a cloud was between the orb formation and decided to take a picture of the orbs. the orbs were bright white and glowing but did not emit a noise, light, or cause any other trouble. i have travelled this same route numerous times at the same time at night and have never seen it before or since. the whole ordeal lasted approximately 45 minutes to an hour. the orbs stayed exactly the same and i decided to go home. i didn't feel nervous, scared, or anxious. i just felt curious and interested.
content.summary: 3 bright white hovering orbs in triangle formation

content.detailedDescription:
i was driving home from work around midnight and i heard on the radio that a lot of people were reporting to local media that a large object was seen over the east coast region and was determined to be a bolide (meteor). i was interested in astronomy and was intrigued by this but didn't give it much thought at the time.

i had been on the highway near my home and got off the next exit and as i was going under an underpass i noticed my car engine cut-out for just a split second as i was accelerating. i noticed this because my car had never done anything like this before.

as i proceeded westbound on the road near my house i noticed a formation of orange lights in the distance ahead over the treetops, i would estimate at the time about 1-1.5 miles distant. at first i surmised it was from the lights of the local tv station tower due to the formation i observed, but quickly realized the direction was wrong.

on a whim, i decided to continue past the turn-off to my neighborhood on the right and continue west just to get a closer look at these lights. even back then,(i was about 18 and i had read a few ufo books like 'interrupted journey' and 'incident at exeter') so i checked my watch for the time.

well, as i left the populated area and headed out into what was then farmland i looked up and over the field near the road i realized the lights were right there over my car (at about 70 degrees elevation) and much closer than i expected. also, i observed that they had been moving slowly to the south, they now appeared to be hovering over a freshly plowed field at 500-1000 feet altitude.

this formation was a trapezoidal configuration with two objects in the front and two others following slightly farther apart in the rear,(all were orange). i panicked and made a sharp right turn at the intersection under the objects and floored my car down the road (i'm still kicking myself for bugging-out so quick).

as i fled the scene i looked over my shoulder to the left, or maybe in my rear-view mirror and i distinctly saw the four objects had come closer together and were descending rapidly towards the ground. that was the last i saw of them, but it is not the end of the story.

i drove down some back roads planning to head home and was struck by the fact that there were no other cars on any of the roads on which i was driving. i had been totally alone even though it was a friday night and traffic should have been heavier.

after i got home i was scared and told my father and brother what i had seen, but my brother said it was probably just a bunch of helicopters.

later, my family got a phone call from my aunt saying my grandmother had been admitted to the hospital and she passed away about two weeks later, (strange coincidence).

anyway, the very next day i was standing in line at the local fast-food restaurant and i saw a girl i knew there. so i asked her if she had seen anything unusual the night before? her eyes bugged out and she said,"did you see those four orange lights too?". i said i did and she told me that she and her friends had been at the local drive-in movie theater nearby when the lights passed overhead. and "everybody stopped watching the movie and got out of their cars to look at what they were".

so i at least had some validation of my sighting. i also dragged my brother and a friend out to the spot to look for landing traces in the freshly plowed fields, but there were none.
content.summary: Orange lights observed much closer than expected.

content.detailedDescription: This was in korssund, west coast of norway 20 feb 2016. it was 4 at night, i woke up because i was thirsty. got out of bed, went to the kitchen, got a glas of water.. looked out of the window, just for a few moments then a huge fireball fell stright down towards the sea, then it just stopped like 100-150 meters over the water for a 2-3 seconds and went stright up agian into space. i was shocked. i have wanted to see something like this for a long time now! and just in matter of seconds there it was. that was not from this earth! made not a sound, it was on fire, it was huge!
content.summary: It was night, saw a big fireball

content.detailedDescription: I had just finished watching a movie and i layed in my bed and put my head phones on. there is a window right in front of my bed and i looked out the window because i notice mars and a few other stars and thinking about how crazy bright mars looked right now. as i'm looking at it i see a white light with red and blue lights blinking on it flying by. i thought it was just a plane but what really caught my attention and made me get up and run to the window was how fast the object was moving. i have never seen a plane or anything for that matter move that fast before. also what i thought was odd was how big the light was. at the size of the light and the distance, usually if it was a plane you should be able to see some detail at that point. like oh okay, i see the blue and red strobes on the wings. but nope, it was just a ball of light. i watch it go behind some trees, still going very very fast, and as it emerged from the trees i noticed a smaller white light following it at the exact same speed. then all of a sudden just before it flew out of sight, i noticed the two lights were connected and that what i was actually looking at was a huge black triangle craft with lights at the points. this freaked me out pretty good and i think i almost had a panic attack. as soon as i lost sight of it i ran downstairs and outside to try and see it, but it was completely gone. which is also weird because in the 20 seconds or so it took me to get downstairs, even if it was really far away it still should have been in sight. but it was gone. i was pretty freaked out after the more and more i thought about it, but also cool.
content.summary: Glowing white light, actually a large triangle craft.

content.detailedDescription:

as usual i was standing on my back porch and gazing around aimlessly while chatting. had i been paying less attention i may have never even noticed what was going on right in front of my eyes. i'd assume the 3 orbs started behind the mountain south of me. the 3 started in a row. if it was one solid craft, i'd describe the first manuever that was performed as a 180. they all continued shifting position like a helicopter escorting high profile persons. they followed a straight line path that went higher and higher until it left the atmosphere and visual range
content.summary: 3 white orbs shifting position

content.detailedDescription: I am going to address more than one event here. the picture with the two ufo is a one time event. this happened over the cow pasture nextdoor to me. i was taking pictures of the clouds and did not notice them until later when i uploaded from ds card to my computer. i enlarged and adjusted contrast a little. the forked tailed one is quite clear the other is fuzzy due to the cloud cover and looks like it may be a drone of sorts. there has been a steady sound of a static/frenquecy noises, day and night. sounds of something running, engines or something. ground vibrates or rocks. i get sensations of falling or of being turned or being lifted. the house and ground are vibrating as i type this. i will address the clouds here before i get to the rest of the show that has been going on. the shapes range from chevrons, triangle, long cylinders with a shark like head on one end. then there are the creature shapes, dragons.Demonic looking entities some have or a kind of weird deformity. they go into one another and also exit. i have seen them meet in a large group like they are discussing something and leave in different directions. i can hear them speaking sometimes but they sound far off and metallic. they have acknowledged me on occasion and i them. i always have my camera and binoculars with me so i started looking a little closer. i believe  they are coming to the ground by way of the trees. some are using what seems to be giant nets up at the tree tops. they walk down right out of tree tops. hammock like areas in the pine trees and dense green leaves like a blind in the others. all seem to be more active at night. at night the terrain will change buildings appear and walkways open up in the trees. sometimes a giant entity will turn a tree, tip it over at its roots and little people come out. they can be under piles of debris too. singing is someting that i hear almost night, always a song i have orcistxever heard before. there are some that look like they are made of vegation, branches and dirt. then there are the robotic, insect, the little browm people,etc. i wish i could draw. i did get some night pictures, sometimes you can not see them but the camera can. i feel the energy they are giving off, it is not a good feeling. recently i somehow end up with thorn, look like little arrow headsin my skin, scratches and bite marks. the barn roof is going to fall in, they are jumping on it, another one has a machete and he can be heard chopping branches with it. most of the trees here are getting brown and or big holes in the foliage. i feel this stuff is all connected i have photos and witness. tell me , should i be calling a priest too? most of these pics were taken by me on my nikon coolpix, nothing fancy. i really would like it if you could send someone in person to see first hand,this is no joke and i am getting a bit worried. thank you erica and my dog sage(she sees them too)
content.summary: I was taking pictures of clouds, they have been really strange lately. two ufo were in this picture. one is on the edge of the cloud covered ship, the other one is right there in broad daylight.
